<PageShell eyebrow="Press" title="Tell Leicester’s space story." intro="Media, contributors and partners can find the essential details for clear, accurate coverage here."><h2>Media enquiries</h2><p>For interview requests, press accreditation, approved logos or a project briefing, contact <a href="mailto:press@leicesterspaceweek.com">press@leicesterspaceweek.com</a>.</p><h2>About Leicester Space Week</h2><p>Leicester Space Week is a citywide platform for space innovation, sustainability, skills, culture and public engagement. It brings together the city’s research, industry and civic communities around a shared future-facing programme.</p></PageShell>
